<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Suvarna Ganta — Solutions Analyst &amp; Business Analyst</title>
<meta name="description" content="Suvarna Ganta is a Solutions Analyst with 5+ years bridging business stakeholders, product, and engineering across e-commerce, blockchain, and digital product operations. Currently at PurpleTalk India, supporting Panini America.">
<meta name="keywords" content="Solutions Analyst, Business Analyst, Product Analyst, Customer Success, Requirements Gathering, Agile, UAT, Suvarna Ganta">
<meta property="og:title" content="Suvarna Ganta — Solutions Analyst & Business Analyst">
<meta property="og:description" content="5+ years bridging business, customers, and engineering across e-commerce, blockchain, and digital product operations.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --teal:#8B7CF6;
    --teal-dim:#8B7CF633;
    --amber:#C7A8F0;
    --amber-dim:#C7A8F033;
    --radius:14px;
    --maxw:1120px;
    color-scheme: dark;
  }
  html[data-theme="dark"]{
    --bg:#120F1E;
    --surface:#1A1530;
    --surface-2:#150F26;
    --border:#2E2650;
    --text:#EDE9F7;
    --text-dim:#A79CC7;
    --text-faint:#6B5F91;
    --shadow: 0 20px 60px -20px rgba(30,10,60,0.55);
  }
  html[data-theme="light"]{
    color-scheme: light;
    --bg:#F7F4FC;
    --surface:#FFFFFF;
    --surface-2:#F0EAFA;
    --border:#E2D8F5;
    --text:#1D1730;
    --text-dim:#645A80;
    --text-faint:#9A8FB8;
    --shadow: 0 20px 60px -20px rgba(90,60,160,0.16);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--bg);
    background-image: radial-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 26px 26px;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    color:var(--text);
    font-family:'IBM Plex Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    transition:background .35s ease, color .35s ease;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  ::selection{ background:var(--teal-dim); color:var(--text); }
  a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
  img{max-width:100%; display:block;}
  .wrap{ max-width:var(--maxw); margin:0 auto; padding:0 28px; }
  .mono{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; }
  h1,h2,h3,h4{ font-family:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; letter-spacing:-0.01em; font-weight:600; }
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:0.14em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--text-faint);
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{
    content:"";
    width:18px; height:1px;
    background:var(--teal);
    display:inline-block;
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    *{ animation-duration:0.001ms !important; animation-iteration-count:1 !important; transition-duration:0.001ms !important; scroll-behavior:auto !important; }
  }

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  header{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100;
    background:color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 82%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  nav{
    max-width:var(--maxw); margin:0 auto; padding:16px 28px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
  }
  .brand{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:18px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
  }
  .brand .dot{ width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--teal); box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--teal-dim); }
  .navlinks{ display:flex; gap:28px; font-size:14px; color:var(--text-dim); }
  .navlinks a{ transition:color .2s ease; position:relative; }
  .navlinks a:hover, .navlinks a:focus-visible{ color:var(--text); }
  .navlinks a:focus-visible{ outline:2px solid var(--teal); outline-offset:4px; border-radius:4px; }
  .navactions{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
  .themebtn{
    width:38px; height:38px; border-radius:50%;
    border:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--surface);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; cursor:pointer;
    color:var(--text);
  }
  .themebtn:focus-visible{ outline:2px solid var(--teal); outline-offset:2px; }
  .btn{
    font-family:'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.02em;
    padding:11px 18px; border-radius:9px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    background:var(--surface);
    cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s ease;
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  }
  .btn:hover{ border-color:var(--teal); transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .btn:focus-visible{ outline:2px solid var(--teal); outline-offset:2px; }
  .btn-primary{ background:var(--teal); border-color:var(--teal); color:#F5F7FF; font-weight:600; }
  .btn-primary:hover{ filter:brightness(1.08); }
  .navmobile{ display:none; }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero{ padding:96px 0 64px; position:relative; }
  .hero::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; top:-120px; right:-160px; width:640px; height:640px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, var(--teal-dim) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter:blur(10px); pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
  }
  .hero::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; bottom:-160px; left:-120px; width:420px; height:420px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, var(--amber-dim) 0%, transparent 72%);
    filter:blur(10px); pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
  }
  .hero .wrap{ position:relative; z-index:1; }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr; gap:56px; align-items:center;
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(34px, 4.6vw, 54px); line-height:1.08; margin:18px 0 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 .accent{ color:var(--teal); }
  .hero p.lede{
    font-size:17px; line-height:1.65; color:var(--text-dim); max-width:52ch; margin-bottom:32px;
  }
  .hero-ctas{ display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .hero-meta{
    display:flex; gap:26px; margin-top:40px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .hero-meta div{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size:12px; color:var(--text-faint); }
  .hero-meta strong{ display:block; font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:22px; color:var(--text); font-weight:700; }

  /* translator widget — signature element */
  .translator{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:18px;
    padding:22px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .translator::before{
    content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:radial-gradient(600px circle at 100% 0%, var(--teal-dim), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .translator-head{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .translator-head .mono{ font-size:11px; color:var(--text-faint); letter-spacing:0.1em; }
  .pulse{ width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--teal); animation:pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse{ 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:0.35;} }
  .t-card{
    background:var(--surface-2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:16px;
    min-height:92px;
  }
  .t-label{ font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.12em; color:var(--text-faint); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .t-label.left{ color:var(--amber); }
  .t-label.right{ color:var(--teal); }
  .t-text{ font-size:14px; line-height:1.5; color:var(--text); min-height:60px; }
  .t-arrow{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin:10px 0; gap:8px;
    color:var(--text-faint); font-size:11px;
  }
  .t-arrow svg{ width:16px; height:16px; }
  .t-dots{ display:flex; gap:6px; justify-content:center; margin-top:16px; }
  .t-dots span{ width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--border); transition:background .3s; }
  .t-dots span.active{ background:var(--teal); }

  /* ---------- PHOTO ---------- */
  .hero-photo-chip{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:14px;
    margin-bottom:22px; padding:7px 20px 7px 7px;
    border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:99px; background:var(--surface);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .hero-photo-chip img{
    width:56px; height:56px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center 15%;
    border:2px solid var(--teal);
    box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--teal-dim);
  }
  .hero-photo-chip .chip-text strong{ display:block; font-size:14px; font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; }
  .hero-photo-chip .chip-text span{ display:block; font-size:11px; color:var(--text-faint); font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; margin-top:2px; }
  .about-avatar-wrap{ position:relative; width:132px; height:132px; margin-bottom:22px; }
  .about-avatar{
    width:132px; height:132px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center 15%;
    border:3px solid var(--surface);
    box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--teal), 0 0 0 9px var(--teal-dim);
    display:block;
  }
  .about-avatar-badge{
    position:absolute; bottom:2px; right:2px; width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--teal); border:3px solid var(--surface);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#fff;
  }

  /* ---------- CASE STUDY ---------- */
  .case-study{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:20px;
    padding:44px; overflow:hidden; position:relative;
  }
  .case-top{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:24px; margin-bottom:36px; }
  .case-top h3{ font-size:clamp(20px,2.6vw,28px); max-width:36ch; }
  .case-result{
    text-align:right; flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .case-result .kpi-num{ font-size:44px; }
  .case-result .kpi-label{ max-width:22ch; margin-left:auto; }
  .case-tags{ display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:14px; }
  .case-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:18px; }
  .case-block{ border-top:2px solid var(--teal); padding-top:16px; }
  .case-block .case-label{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.1em; color:var(--text-faint); margin-bottom:10px; }
  .case-block p{ font-size:14px; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.65; }
  .case-block:nth-child(2){ border-top-color:var(--amber); }
  .case-block:nth-child(4){ border-top-color:var(--amber); }

  /* ---------- SECTION shell ---------- */
  section{ padding:88px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  section:first-of-type{ border-top:none; }
  .sec-head{ margin-bottom:44px; max-width:640px; }
  .sec-badge{
    width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:11px;
    background:var(--teal-dim); color:var(--teal);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:14px; border:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .sec-head h2{ font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,36px); margin-top:14px; }
  .sec-head p{ color:var(--text-dim); margin-top:12px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; }
  .reveal{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease; }
  .reveal.in{ opacity:1; transform:none; }

  /* ---------- ABOUT ---------- */
  .about-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:0.85fr 1.15fr; gap:56px; align-items:start; }
  .about-card{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; padding:26px;
  }
  .about-card h4{ font-size:14px; color:var(--text-faint); margin-bottom:14px; letter-spacing:0.04em; }
  .role-row{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:9px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); font-size:14px; }
  .role-row:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }
  .role-row span:first-child{ color:var(--text-dim); }
  .role-row span:last-child{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:13px; }
  .about-text p{ color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:18px; font-size:15.5px; }
  .about-text strong{ color:var(--text); font-weight:600; }
  .pill-row{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:22px; }
  .pill{
    font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:11.5px; padding:6px 12px;
    border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:99px; color:var(--text-dim);
  }

  /* ---------- EXPERIENCE TIMELINE ---------- */
  .timeline{ position:relative; padding-left:28px; }
  .timeline::before{
    content:""; position:absolute; left:5px; top:6px; bottom:6px; width:1px; background:var(--border);
  }
  .t-item{ position:relative; padding-bottom:48px; }
  .t-item:last-child{ padding-bottom:0; }
  .t-item::before{
    content:""; position:absolute; left:-28px; top:4px; width:11px; height:11px; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--bg); border:2px solid var(--teal);
  }
  .t-item.dim::before{ border-color:var(--text-faint); }
  .t-top{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .t-role{ font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; }
  .t-date{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; color:var(--text-faint); }
  .t-org{ color:var(--teal); font-size:14px; margin-bottom:14px; font-weight:500; }
  .t-org .client{ color:var(--text-faint); }
  .t-bullets{ list-style:none; }
  .t-bullets li{
    position:relative; padding-left:18px; color:var(--text-dim); font-size:14.5px; line-height:1.65; margin-bottom:9px;
  }
  .t-bullets li::before{
    content:"—"; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--text-faint);
  }
  .t-projects{ display:flex; gap:10px; margin-top:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .t-proj-tag{
    font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; padding:5px 10px; border-radius:7px;
    background:var(--amber-dim); color:var(--amber); border:1px solid var(--amber-dim);
  }

  /* ---------- PRODUCTS ---------- */
  .products-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:24px; }
  .product-card{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; padding:28px;
    position:relative; overflow:hidden; transition:transform .25s ease, border-color .25s ease;
  }
  .product-card:hover{ transform:translateY(-4px); border-color:var(--teal); }
  .product-tag{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:var(--text-faint); letter-spacing:0.08em; margin-bottom:14px; display:block; }
  .product-card h3{ font-size:22px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .product-card p{ color:var(--text-dim); font-size:14.5px; line-height:1.65; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .product-feats{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
  .feat{ font-size:11.5px; font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; color:var(--text-dim); background:var(--surface-2); border-radius:7px; padding:5px 10px; }

  /* ---------- COMPETENCIES ---------- */
  .comp-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:14px; }
  .comp-group{ background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; padding:22px; }
  .comp-group h4{ font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color:var(--amber); margin-bottom:14px; font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; }
  .comp-group ul{ list-style:none; }
  .comp-group li{ font-size:14px; color:var(--text-dim); padding:6px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed var(--border); }
  .comp-group li:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }

  /* ---------- ACHIEVEMENTS / KPI ---------- */
  .kpi-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:16px; }
  .kpi-card{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; padding:24px 20px;
    text-align:left;
  }
  .kpi-num{ font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:36px; font-weight:700; color:var(--teal); margin-bottom:6px; }
  .kpi-label{ font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.4; }
  .ach-list{ margin-top:28px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px 32px; }
  .ach-list li{ list-style:none; font-size:14.5px; color:var(--text-dim); padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; gap:10px; }
  .ach-list li::before{ content:"✓"; color:var(--teal); font-weight:700; }

  /* ---------- WORK PROCESS ---------- */
  .process{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr); gap:12px; counter-reset:step; }
  .step{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; padding:20px 16px;
    position:relative;
  }
  .step .num{ font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; color:var(--text-faint); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .step h4{ font-size:14.5px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .step p{ font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.5; }
  .step-arrow{ display:none; }

  /* ---------- CONTACT ---------- */

  .contact-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px; }
  .contact-card{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; padding:22px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px;
  }
  a.contact-card{ transition:transform .2s ease, border-color .2s ease; cursor:pointer; }
  a.contact-card:hover{ transform:translateY(-3px); border-color:var(--teal); }
  a.contact-card:focus-visible{ outline:2px solid var(--teal); outline-offset:2px; }
  .contact-icon{ width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:10px; background:var(--teal-dim); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:var(--teal); flex-shrink:0; }
  .contact-card .label{ font-size:11px; color:var(--text-faint); font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; margin-bottom:3px; }
  .contact-card .value{ font-size:14.5px; font-weight:500; }

  footer{ border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding:32px 0; }
  footer .wrap{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; }
  footer p{ font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-faint); font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace; }

  /* ---------- RESPONSIVE ---------- */
  @media (max-width:900px){
    .navlinks{ display:none; }
    .hero-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .about-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .products-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .comp-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .kpi-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .process{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .contact-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .ach-list{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .case-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .case-result{ text-align:left; }
    .case-result .kpi-label{ margin-left:0; }
  }
  @media (max-width:560px){
    .comp-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .kpi-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .process{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    section{ padding:60px 0; }
    .hero{ padding:56px 0 40px; }
    .case-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .case-study{ padding:28px 22px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav>
    <div class="brand"><span class="dot"></span> Suvarna Ganta</div>
    <div class="navlinks">
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
      <a href="#products">Products</a>
      <a href="#case-study">Case Study</a>
      <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
      <a href="#achievements">Achievements</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <div class="navactions">
      <button class="themebtn" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Toggle dark and light mode">
        <svg id="iconMoon" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/></svg>
        <svg id="iconSun" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display:none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"/></svg>
      </button>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Hire me</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="top" style="border-top:none;">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-photo-chip">
          <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Suvarna Ganta">
          <div class="chip-text">
            <strong>Suvarna Ganta</strong>
            <span>SOLUTIONS ANALYST</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="eyebrow">SOLUTIONS ANALYST · HYDERABAD, INDIA</div>
        <h1>I close the gap between<br>what the business wants and <span class="accent">what gets built.</span></h1>
        <p class="lede">Suvarna Ganta bridges stakeholders, product, and engineering — 5+ years across e-commerce, blockchain, and digital product operations at PurpleTalk India, supporting Panini America.</p>
